<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>等待 on 大大的小蜗牛</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/tags/%E7%AD%89%E5%BE%85/</link><description>Recent content in 等待 on 大大的小蜗牛</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><copyright>© 2006 - 2024 &lt;span class='inline-block'>&lt;a href='https://www.eallion.com/copyright/' target='_blank'>eallion.com&lt;/a> All Rights Reserved&lt;/span>. &lt;span class='inline-block'>&lt;a href='https://beian.miit.gov.cn/' target='_blank'>浙ICP备16031768号-2&lt;/a>&lt;/span></copyright><lastBuildDate>Wed, 17 Dec 2008 21:38:11 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.eallion.com/tags/%E7%AD%89%E5%BE%85/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>感觉像是等什么的过了一天</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/so-what-feels-like-over-a-day/</link><pubDate>Wed, 17 Dec 2008 21:38:11 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/so-what-feels-like-over-a-day/</guid><description>文章讲述了作者一天的经历，他感觉像是在等待着什么。早上醒来后感到有点难受，但这只是小问题。作者认为今天与以往不同，这种感觉与人有关。文章提到数字花园和用爱发电的概念。</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/so-what-feels-like-over-a-day/featured.png"/></item><item><title>淡淡的</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/light/</link><pubDate>Tue, 25 Nov 2008 23:03:24 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/light/</guid><description>这篇文章介绍了一种人感到寂寞时的内心独白。作者以淡淡的情绪表达了他对某人的思念，但这是一种不能告诉对方的情感。除了自娱自乐，作者只能等待，他乐观开朗的样子只是为了给别人看。而对于自己来说，内心充满了寂寞。作者认识到自己唯一能做的就是让这种寂寞慢慢消失。</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/light/featured.png"/></item><item><title>等待</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/wait/</link><pubDate>Thu, 20 Nov 2008 22:36:46 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/wait/</guid><description>文章讲述了作者在等待中花费了太多时间和精力，但往往没有什么结果。他意识到自己是在等待时已经过去了。</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/wait/featured.png"/></item></channel></rss>